                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 711.38/38.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Davis</persName> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-10-06T16:00:00-04:49">
                                    <hi rend="italic">October 6, 1915—4 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Chamber of Deputies voted ratification this afternoon 75 to 6.</p>
                        <closer>
